{"tid":2306842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老人家跌親好易死！隨時影響世界！","createTime":"2020-11-30T17:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T20:50:09.000Z","uid":219635,"like":130,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"b376ae379aa664a7e61cbc4a579ef7badfaef081","tid":2306842,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">拜登右腳些微骨裂或須穿助行鞋幾星期</span><br />\n<br />\n「港台」美國總統當選人拜登在與他的一隻狗玩期間扭傷右腳，經電腦掃瞄後發現有些微骨裂，醫生建議他穿助行鞋幾星期，作為防護。<br />\n<br />\n拜登的辦公室說，拜登當地星期六下午扭傷，並在特拉華州接受骨科醫生檢查。醫生表示，最初的X光檢查並沒有發現明顯骨折，但接受進一步電腦掃瞄時，發現拜登腳部有兩處輕微骨裂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人老骨頭脆，咁少事都隨時做「癱妃」會唔會早少少收檔？<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562736-20201130.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562736-20201130.htm&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xIL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=716539b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562736-20201130.htm&h=3073bce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562736-20201130.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f26a74dfc6861b2458476e274d0344d0774507c1","tid":2306842,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:25:52.000Z","msg":"健康問題？退選？"},{"pid":"811a9bc95516bb224e47f98be87fbdef767c5a3a","tid":2306842,"uid":219635,"like":118,"dislike":6,"score":112,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:25:53.000Z","msg":"同隻狗玩下，散步都咁唔小心，仲點交成個國家比佢？"},{"pid":"da35fa1bfb00edfad4b57bb96cbe72d9445a4a71","tid":2306842,"uid":219635,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f26a74dfc6861b2458476e274d0344d0774507c1","tid":2306842,"uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:25:52.000Z","msg":"健康問題？退選？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T17:26:26.000Z","msg":"殉職"},{"pid":"3ebd9e3a8b832eee50cca82f351e960dfafe3801","tid":2306842,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11