 />\n人老骨頭脆，咁少事都隨時做「癱妃」會唔會早少少收檔？<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562736-20201130.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562736-20201130.htm&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xIL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=716539b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562736-20201130.htm&h=3073bce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562736-20201130.htm</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T23:57:21.000Z","msg":"拜登生過腦瘤，瘤汁已經溢出<br />\n其實佢已經半廢狀態，靠奧巴馬幕後操縱<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Biden#Brain_surgeries\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FJoe_Biden%23Brain_surgeries&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xIL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=020e9b27\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Biden#Brain_surgeries</a><br />\n<ins>Brain surgeries</ins><br />\nIn February 1988, after several episodes of increasingly severe neck pain, Biden was taken by ambulance to Walter Reed Army Medical Center for surgery to correct a leaking intracranial berry aneurysm.  While recuperating he suffered a pulmonary embolism, a serious complication.<br />\nAfter a second aneurysm was surgically repaired in May, Biden's recuperation kept him away from the Senate for seven months."},{"pid":"dc5f8778dfa1a32469b8c260b9ad3127f37c9947","tid":2306842,"uid":127575,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T23:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kVjVyns.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVjVyns.jpg&h=d17819a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b89db7478820eb5fe7b6e3942a92b90c88a0c43","tid":2306842,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T00:02:33.000Z","msg":"行唔行到空軍一號條樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12f19cc6afa235e3ce266df8ff96